{"tid":654623,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［廣東話改詞］毒撚之歌  （改：稻香）","createTime":"2018-05-05T19:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T05:51:42.000Z","uid":58474,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0a66a0c62e4073da845dc229f833db45002443","tid":654623,"uid":58474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:34:24.000Z","msg":"夜漸覺惆悵  人海之中都不帶歡暢<br />\n扮無恙  問哪位可知曉真相<br />\n亦同樣  毒撚之歌有哪個  欣賞<br />\n<br />\n注意談吐及禮儀着長褲  論品性且善良亦可以惹人惡<br />\n回首也未見有看顧<br />\n毒得辛苦  日落更是堅固<br />\n<br />\n望身邊青蛙烏鴉都不堪逗留  哪個廝守可給拉拉衣袖<br />\n淚滲透  在世間只得我出醜<br />\n揭開窗都可趕走天邊的星宿  獨個的偷走  都市的荒謬<br />\n夜變晝  直播孤單的某某<br />\n<br />\n接受再次湧現照常鬥志  我卻在倒置<br />\n故振作正欲試  被看到笑道引嗤<br />\n做事按着本份破額斷翅  嘆俗態碰上破格的放肆<br />\n<br />\n有意無意  百物合唱雨後將至<br />\n靜細聽呱啦呱啦  愈聽愈覺真摰<br />\n大地漸回暖意  剩下我未換上新枝<br />\n<br />\nWhat is this for <br />\nI got zero and no more , oh therefore<br />\nI am that poor like boar, no one adore<br />\nhow can I get score<br />\n<br />\n就寧願不變故 穿短褲 框一副 自帶污 <br />\n哦哦～盛宴派對以食作伴靜似枯<br />\n哦哦～默離去向後退算是我天賦<br />\n毒得辛苦  日落更是堅固<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多rap, 可能有少少教會feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要微tune<br />\n有一段用左英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a4c50890241acae11511f8f58bb6f29203c94ce","tid":654623,"uid":110876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/110848_a0cdcd99006b0bc8e287a88369ef8b34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F110848_a0cdcd99006b0bc8e287a88369ef8b34.jpg&h=80a70933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e1babf2f1e505a09378a9837b22a965256cda85","tid":654623,"uid":86684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"唔錯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0443bf7cc7d7d756a30b56a0b893f9d5485c542a","tid":65462